               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Have you the check? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—I got it from the bankers.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
